<paragraph blockId="2.[151,666,1086,1149]" box="[151,223,1123,1149]" pageId="2" pageNumber="217">
<figureCitation box="[151,220,1123,1149]" captionStart="FIGURE 2" captionStartId="4.[151,250,1841,1865]" captionTargetBox="[171,1413,198,1800]" captionTargetId="figure-26@4.[157,1430,181,1817]" captionTargetPageId="4" captionText="FIGURE 2. Macropsis (Macropsis) koreana sp. nov. A: male, dorsal view of a body, B: lateral view of male, C: head in facial, D: tergal apodemes of 2nd abdominal base, E: sternal apodemes of 2nd abdominal base, F: pygofer appendage in lateral aspect, G: aedeagus in lateral aspect, H: style in lateral aspect. Scale bar = 1.0 mm (A–E); 0.1 mm (F–J)." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5627201" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5627201/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="217">Fig. 2</figureCitation>
